{"pageProps":{"eyebrow":"eunomia-bpf","page":{"layout":"document","title":"ecli","description":"ecli is the local eunomia-bpf CLI for loading, running, pulling, and pushing precompiled programs.","bodyHtml":"<p><code>ecli</code> is the local eunomia-bpf CLI for loading, running, pulling, and pushing precompiled programs.</p>\n<p>The legacy remote HTTP mode (<code>ecli client</code> / <code>ecli-server</code>) has been removed from the main branch to reduce maintenance overhead. The last implementation is preserved on the <code>archive/ecli-remote-http</code> branch.</p>\n<h2 id=\"usage\">Usage</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\"> &#x3C;</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\">COMMAN</span><span style=\"color:#ADBAC7\">D</span><span style=\"color:#F47067\">></span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"examples\">Examples</h2>\n<p>Run the eBPF program as wasm or json.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># run with wasm bpf modules</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> runqlat.wasm</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#768390\"># run with json bpf object only</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> package.json</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>Or run the eBPF program as a tar file that contains minimal BTF info and a BPF object.</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> client.tar</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>The <code>ecc</code> packaged tar contains custom BTF files and <code>package.json</code>, which can be run on older kernels.</p>\n<p>For details, see <a href=\"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/#options\">ecc-btfgen</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"commands\">Commands</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>run - Run the ebpf program as tar or json.</li>\n<li>push - Push a container to an OCI registry.</li>\n<li>pull - Pull a container from an OCI registry.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"install\">Install</h2>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">wget</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://aka.pw/bpf-ecli</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> -O</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ecli</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">chmod</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> +x</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"github-pages-and-url-examples\">GitHub Pages and URL examples</h2>\n<p>The historical GitHub Pages workflow is still kept for compatibility:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://eunomia-bpf.github.io/eunomia-bpf/sigsnoop/package.json</span></span>\n<span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> https://eunomia-bpf.github.io/eunomia-bpf/sigsnoop/app.wasm</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<h2 id=\"oci-examples\">OCI examples</h2>\n<p>Pull an image locally:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> pull</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ghcr.io/eunomia-bpf/execve:latest</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>Run directly from the registry:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">sudo</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> run</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ghcr.io/eunomia-bpf/execve:latest</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>Push a Wasm module:</p>\n<figure data-rehype-pretty-code-figure=\"\"><pre tabindex=\"0\" data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\"><code data-language=\"bash\" data-theme=\"github-dark-dimmed\" style=\"display: grid;\"><span data-line=\"\"><span style=\"color:#F69D50\">./ecli</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> push</span><span style=\"color:#6CB6FF\"> --module</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> app.wasm</span><span style=\"color:#96D0FF\"> ghcr.io/yourorg/mytool:v1.0</span></span></code></pre></figure>\n<p>For historical notes about the removed remote mode, see <a href=\"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/\">ecli server</a>.</p>","headings":[{"id":"usage","text":"Usage","depth":2},{"id":"examples","text":"Examples","depth":2},{"id":"commands","text":"Commands","depth":2},{"id":"install","text":"Install","depth":2},{"id":"github-pages-and-url-examples","text":"GitHub Pages and URL examples","depth":2},{"id":"oci-examples","text":"OCI examples","depth":2}],"sourcePath":"https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia.dev/tree/main/docs/eunomia-bpf/ecli/index.md","metadata":{"updatedAt":"2026-03-08T04:58:07.000Z","createdAt":"2023-08-10T12:54:12.000Z","authors":[{"name":"云微","email":"1067852565@qq.com"},{"name":"oluceps","email":"ospp@oluceps.uk"}]},"path":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","alternates":{"en":"/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","zh":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/"},"continuation":{"index":{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","description":"![GitHub release (latest by date)](https://github.com/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/releases) ![codecov](https://codecov.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf) ![DeepSource](https://deepsource.io/gh/eunomia-bpf/eunomia-bpf/?ref=reposi","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/"},"previous":{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","description":"bpf 运行时需要有Linux内核相关支持，docker 中的内核共享的宿主机的内核，因此使用docker运行bpf程序时需要使用以下命令为容器赋予权限和相关内核支持。","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/"},"next":{"title":"ecli server","description":"ecli-server 和 ecli client 子命令已在 2026 年 3 月从主分支移除，以降低维护复杂度。","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/"}},"sidebar":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","items":[{"title":"eunomia-bpf：简化并增强eBPF，支持CO-RE[^1]和WebAssembly[^2]","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/","depth":0},{"title":"Project architecture","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/architecture/","depth":1},{"title":"benchmark","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/benchmark/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc docker usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/docker-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"github template","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/github-template/","depth":2},{"title":"eunomia-cc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/","depth":1},{"title":"ecc usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecc/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli dockerfile usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/ecli-dockerfile-usage/","depth":2},{"title":"ecli","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/","depth":1},{"title":"ecli server","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/ecli/server/","depth":2},{"title":"exporter","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/","depth":1},{"title":"usage","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/exporter/usage/","depth":2},{"title":"introduction","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/introduction/","depth":1},{"title":"eunomia-bpf 用户手册: 让 eBPF 程序的开发和部署尽可能简单","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/manual/","depth":1},{"title":"在线体验网站","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/online/","depth":1},{"title":"quickstart","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/quickstart/","depth":1},{"title":"build on android aarch64","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build-android-arm/","depth":2},{"title":"build from source","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/build/","depth":2},{"title":"Install ecli and ecc","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/setup/","depth":1},{"title":"supporting-external-BTF","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/supporting-external-BTF/","depth":1},{"title":"video","href":"/zh/eunomia-bpf/video/","depth":1}]}]}},"__N_SSG":true}